insights: Master dependency tracking system for 2025 planning with read-only mastersheet and editable alliance-specific tabs
Process includes acceptance workflow where recipient alliances must manually update acceptance status
Once accepted, dependencies must be copied to recipient's roadmap as strategies
Rejections are automatically communicated back to requestors via their roadmap's DependencyLog tab
System has built-in lag time (1-2 hours) for data synchronization across sheets
Clear separation between Tech and Non-Tech team alliances for dependency management
FAQs indicate common issues: editing restrictions (only acceptance status should be modified), communication protocols, and removal procedures
Recent email activity shows coordination challenges around PA resource alignment for New Ventures, with scheduling conflicts between team meetings
Active JIRA work includes OTP checkout improvements, Statsig metrics, and SAR latency issues (blocked)
GitHub activity shows ongoing work on TPT (The Pets Table) features including quiz tests, portion selection, and calorie adjustments
